channel.title: Project Marcbob - GREAT FORUMS - Fast training & easy money - Lots of features
channel.description:
Welcome to the advertisement thread for Project Marcbob!
[size=15pt][b]Forums: http://marcbob.com
Webclient: http://marcbob.com/play.html
Client download: http://marcbob.com/client.jar[/b][/size]
PMB is currently being ran on a VPS so it is online 24/7. Our base is Matrix and we have turned it into a great economy source. We have already added tons of features, dungeons, bosses, and more! I am no where to being even close to getting started with this source. Lots of updates will be coming.
[b]We do need moderators and support team members![/b]
[IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/mr7o1.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2ebzber.png[/img] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/30v0vvr.png[/img] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/29zaln5.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/f4juaa.png[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/sg1elz.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/2a95kdd.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/wvq135.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/14m97gx.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/1z57zgm.png[/img] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/vi2la9.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2q19wf7.png[/img]
[b]Sorry I know awful pics[/b]
[b]Features:[/b] -Flower Game and Dicing -Lots of Bosses -Original Dungeons with special drops -Custom Items -Great Pking -All Noncb Skills except dungeoneering but you can still obtain chaotics from npcs -Squeal of Fortune -Lots of other matrix features -Fast lvling and training
[size=24pt][b]Website: http://marcbob.com
WEBCLIENT: http://marcbob.com/play.html
Client download: http://marcbob.com/client.jar[/b][/size]
Sorry for bad thread, just got bored today and wanted to run a server again. Gonna be spending lots of time on it - Got tons of stuff I am going to be doing. Check my development team thread here too: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,595539.0.html
